
[Code Quality]
EventHandler:   make event dispatch multi-threaded
Events:         add virtual `char* name() const` function for debug
Log Errors:     make errors more verbose, and include __PRETTY_FUNCTION__

[Feature]
Add `KeyHoldEvent` event triggered if more than one `KeyPressEvent` dispatched successively.
Add `MouseHoldEvent` event triggered if more than one `MousePressEvent` dispatched successively.

Move `Window` and graphics tasks to a dedicated `Graphics` thread.
Promote `EventHandler`s to `Layer`s
